== Command line installation and update scripts ==

The installation and the update may be done by command line interface. To install
aitsu, go to the web root directory and fire following command:

php application/cli/index.php -sInstallation

To update the database structure of an existing installation use following command:

php application/cli/index.php -sUpdate

If you need to run the script with other privileges than the database user that is
used by aitsu, you may specifiy the user and password as follows:

php application/cli/index.php -uroot -pmypassword -sUpdate

Depending on the configuration of mysql super privileges might be necessary to create
views and functions.
